Dawn of War - Warhammer 40,000 Music from DOW, WA and DC

This is the music from Dawn of War - Warhammer 40k, Winter Assault and Dark Crusade!
A fellow Pirate Bay\&#039;er mannahazarika informed me that the music for Winter Assault and Dark Crusade is different from the plain old DOW.  So I\&#039;ve included all of the regular full length tracks and some incidental music.  There are a good amount of variations on the songs below inside the game.  If you are driven to get the additional variations on your favourite races themes go here... <a href="
http://forums.relicnews.com/showthread.php?t=76681" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
http://forums.relicnews.com/showthread.php?t=76681</a>
